      <title>以太币 ETF 有望于 7 月中旬获批</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/ether-etfs-could-get-approval-by-mid-july-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[资产管理者对美国证券交易委员会将批准首批美国 ETF 持乐观态度。彭博社的 Emily Graffeo 在“Bloomberg ETF IQ”节目中接受 Katie Griefeld、Scarlet Fu 和 Eric Balchunas 采访时讨论了费用和需求情况。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/ether-etfs-could-get-approval-by-mid-july-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 17:55:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周股市开盘创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/stocks-kick-off-the-week-at-all-time-highs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市上涨至历史新高，交易员们一边等待财报季的开始，一边关注美国总统竞选以及有关美联储下一步行动的任何线索。Principal Asset Management 首席策略师 Seema Shah 与 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 一起在“彭博科技”上进行讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/stocks-kick-off-the-week-at-all-time-highs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 17:51:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
